

these are the rules of the game
    1: get close to the number 21, without going over"
    2: kings, queens, and jacks of all kinds are worth 10
    3: you can choose whether your 'Ace' is worth 1 or 11
    4: if you hit 21 exactly, you win
    5: if you go over 21 you loose
    6: if you have a higher number than the dealers cards but under 21, you win
    7: if you have a number lower than the dealers cards and under 21, you loose

extra information, you may need to know
    - kings, queens, and jacks of all kinds are worth 10
    - you can choose whether your 'Ace' is worth 1 or 11
    - there are no jokers